{"id":"2f61f862-253e-41b9-a051-ac72bfe36761","name":"ZeBlackBallD Universe","description":"<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">Almost all the characters are over 1000+ years old!</mark></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(96, 0, 255);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">YES, FINALLY, TWO DAYS LATER, I DID IT, BITCH!!!</mark></span></p><hr><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 13);\">\"Wow, a new bot? That fast?\"</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(96, 0, 255);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">\"OF COURSE!\"</mark></span></p><hr><p>I really love cosmic horror, and that's why I really liked <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/ZeBlackBallD\" target=\"_blank\">ZeBlackBallD</a>'s work. For some reason, I couldn't find a single complete bot with the full <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/ZeBlackBallD\" target=\"_blank\">ZeBlackBallD</a> lore online. <em>I'll warn you in advance that the bot isn't finished yet, and there will be more updates in the future.</em></p><hr><p><strong>Characters:</strong><br><br><strong>The Nightmare</strong> and <strong>Jack Krinsberg</strong> (I couldn't find a canon name for him, so I made up my own).<br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/F0ZlTdDD2YMEQXGDaThn1.webp\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/ER9srz2hgHHcCLWhEIxfA.webp\"></p><p><strong>The Flesh God</strong> and <strong>Henry Williams</strong> (her husband)<br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/jWCTB_KEFtetdSShpjOxi.webp\"></p><p><strong>The Calamity</strong><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/gWcIQFIOIA90od0wo1y3H.webp\"></p><p><strong>The Apostle</strong> and <strong>Sarah Morgan</strong> (Sarah is the boss at the office where the Apostle works)</p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/06HcEU1x6KiSm5fy8ELio.webp\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/sedcEmH0E6F-iYISB5zEl.webp\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/BNTjrhUgzwbJKptKkkFpz.webp\"></p><p></p><p><strong>The Gore Bride</strong> (she has a human husband, by the way)<br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/A77cOjfA2sqlOW3z9kYpg.webp\"></p><p><strong>The Manifestor</strong><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/aNbUEbtjsWFkr3UIuoPAW.webp\"></p><p><strong>The Nova</strong><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/cszWmp0xm6QK3yNGK1rlQ.webp\"></p><p><strong>The Gatherer</strong></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/Aup5duhzDA_hzxkebNAoo.webp\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/MW_agV-f30eo63mG0BRmQ.webp\"></p><p><strong>The Guardian</strong><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/pS_mcy2BFTlNRmLn6BG_u.webp\"></p><p><strong>The Mother of Crowns</strong><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/V9VqHb2vURBhZlGl-sZtq.webp\"><br><strong>The Stalker and James Johnson </strong>(<strong>The Stalker's</strong> owner)<br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/u-OArMfP0WvR8FvWAbB4i.webp\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/Q3yqf6fOeckJGD-9b4-2Q.webp\"><br><strong>The Huntress</strong><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/P2UBN1EOso52pi9SHdhAX.webp\"><br><strong>The Dreamweaver</strong> and <strong>Charlotte Adams</strong> (By the way, Charlotte is not his wife, just a woman he often visits)<br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/TQq994A2LlCTkiTc8SxGe.webp\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/apLTNtf7E84PLzG58qaY7.webp\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/iI7beAdT_OYew70vUGTvz.webp\"><br><strong>The Crawler</strong><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/BOBYVmkEK25n1yT6e1adX.webp\"></p><p><strong>The Essence</strong><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitora